      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Adobe Firefly safe for commercial use?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, Adobe Firefly is designed with commercial safety as a core principle. It is trained on licensed content such as Adobe Stock, and Adobe provides indemnification for commercial use, making it the safest choice for businesses concerned about copyright and licensing issues with AI-generated content."
