<h2>1. Canva AI — 🏆 Editor's Choice</h2>
<p>Canva AI is the most accessible all-in-one design platform, making professional design available to everyone. Its AI features — Magic Design (generates complete designs from text), Magic Eraser, AI image generation, Magic Write (AI copywriting), and Brand Kit — are built into an intuitive drag-and-drop interface backed by a library of over 250,000 templates. It handles social media graphics, presentations, flyers, and videos with minimal effort.</p>

<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "Create a social media post for a sustainable fashion brand launch — warm earth tones, minimalist layout, with placeholder text"</p>
<ul>
<li>Magic Design output accuracy: 9/10 — excellent layout generation</li>
<li>Generation time: ~3 seconds for AI design suggestions</li>
<li>Template variety: 10/10 — massive library across all categories</li>
<li>AI image generation quality: 8/10 — good but not best-in-class</li>
</ul>

